testPriorities.description: Domain coordinators and plugins that orchestrate QE operations

recommendations.impact: Core QE orchestration logic is untested, high risk of production issues
recommendations.recommendation: Create comprehensive unit tests for all domain coordinators focusing on task delegation and event handling
Implement integration tests for each protocol (quality-gate, security-audit, defect-investigation, etc.)

recommendations.impact: Memory management and hybrid storage are production-critical
recommendations.recommendation: Add unit tests for memory backend initialization, data persistence, and recovery scenarios

recommendations.impact: Plugin lifecycle and event handling untested
recommendations.recommendation: Create plugin initialization, event subscription, and disposal tests

recommendations.finding: Entire compatibility module (4 files, 1150 statements) has 0% coverage
recommendations.impact: v2 to v3 migration paths are untested
recommendations.recommendation: Add migration scenario tests for config-migrator, agent-mapper, and adapters

recommendations.impact: Core test generation logic partially tested
recommendations.recommendation: Increase coverage of pattern-matcher.ts and test-generator.ts to >80%

recommendations.impact: Coverage gap detection has coverage gaps itself
recommendations.recommendation: Focus on risk-scorer.ts (0% coverage) and sublinear-analyzer.ts edge cases

recommendations.impact: Performance benchmarks not validated by tests
recommendations.recommendation: Create smoke tests to ensure benchmarks run without errors
